The paper discusses paper recommendation algorithms using citation information among papers, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR), digital libraries (cs.DL), and databases (cs.DB). The paper also mentions adapting the algorithms for venue and reviewer recommendation tasks, which are relevant to social networks and information systems (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper mentions using natural language processing techniques, which is a common topic in computational linguistics (cs.CL).
